  ('IntexGlobal','PS2401LB','Glass Fusion Bottle With Bamboo Lid - 600Ml','glass-fusion-bottle-with-bamboo-lid-600ml-ps2401lb','Drinkware','Drink Bottles','The Glass Fusion Bottle with Bamboo Lid is a sleek and sustainable choice for staying hydrated, combining durability and style in a modern design.',50,true,false,'["Durable Borosilicate Glass: Strong and shatterproof for long-lasting use.", "Bamboo Lid with Carry Strap: Features a natural bamboo lid for an eco-friendly touch and a convenient strap for portability.", "Generous Capacity: Holds up to 600ml, perfect for everyday hydration needs.", "Versatile Use: Ideal for water and non-carbonated, non-hot, or non-frozen beverages.", "Eco-Friendly Packaging: Each bottle is individually packed in a sustainable gift box, making it perfect for gifting.", "Handwash Recommended: To maintain the bottle’s integrity and extend its lifespan."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "6.5cm Diameter x 23cm H"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Clear", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps2401lb/ps2401lb-main.webp"}]'::jsonb,null,'supplier',true,false,null,5,'local_stock','Intex','https://www.intexglobal.com/product/glass-fusion-bottle-with-bamboo-lid-600ml/');
