  ('IntexGlobal','PS2501','White Sublimation Mug - 330Ml','white-sublimation-mug-330ml-ps2501','Drinkware','Mugs','Bring your designs to life with the White Sublimation Mug 330ml, a sleek, can-shaped coffee mug crafted to showcase vibrant prints with lasting durability. Ideal for promotional giveaways, personalized gifts, or corporate branding, this mug is the perfect blend of style and functionality.',50,true,false,'["Premium Sublimation Coating: Ensures vibrant, high-resolution prints with enhanced longevity.", "Unique Can Shape Design: A modern and stylish twist on the classic coffee mug.", "Generous 330ml Capacity: Perfect for your favorite coffee, tea, or hot beverage.", "Eco-Friendly Packaging: Individually packed in a sustainable gift box, ideal for thoughtful presentation."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "9.5cm H x 8cm Diameter"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "White", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps2501/ps2501-main.webp"}]'::jsonb,null,'supplier',true,false,null,5,'local_stock','Intex','https://www.intexglobal.com/product/white-sublimation-mug-330ml/');
