  ('IntexGlobal','PS2502','Two Tone Sublimation Mug - 330Ml','two-tone-sublimation-mug-330ml-ps2502','Drinkware','Mugs','The Two Tone Sublimation Mug 330ml, designed to captivate with its striking two-tone colors and vibrant, long-lasting prints. Perfect for personalized gifts, corporate branding, or promotional giveaways, this mug offers a unique combination of style and durability.',50,true,false,'["Two-Tone Design: Features a coloured handle and inner, offering a bold contrast that stands out.", "Sublimation Printing: Ensures vibrant, high-quality prints with enhanced longevity for lasting color.", "Seamless Color Blend: The unique combination of hues creates a captivating visual effect that catches the eye.", "330ml Capacity: Ideal for your favorite hot beverages, from coffee to tea.", "Eco-Friendly Packaging: Individually packed in a sustainable gift box, making it perfect for gifting or promotional purposes."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "9.5cm H x 8cm Diameter"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Black", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps2502/ps2502-black.webp"}, {"name": "Light Blue", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps2502/ps2502-light-blue.webp"}, {"name": "Light Green", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps2502/ps2502-light-green.webp"}, {"name": "Orange", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps2502/ps2502-orange.webp"}, {"name": "Red", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps2502/ps2502-red.webp"}]'::jsonb,null,'supplier',true,false,null,5,'local_stock','Intex','https://www.intexglobal.com/product/two-tone-sublimation-mug-330ml/');
