  ('IntexGlobal','PS2810','Enamel Camping Mug - 325Ml','enamel-camping-mug-325ml-ps2810','Drinkware','Mugs','Introducing our 325ml Enamel Mug, designed for both outdoor adventures and cozy moments at home. This durable and lightweight mug offers the perfect balance of style and practicality.',50,true,false,'["325ml Capacity: Ideal size for enjoying your favorite hot beverages.", "Available in 2 Colours: Choose from a selection of vibrant, eye-catching options.", "Lightweight and Strong: Built for durability and ease of use, perfect for travel or everyday enjoyment."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "8.5cm H x 9cm Diameter"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Black", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps2810/ps2810-black.webp"}, {"name": "White", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps2810/ps2810-white.webp"}]'::jsonb,null,'supplier',true,false,null,5,'local_stock','Intex','https://www.intexglobal.com/product/enamel-camping-mug-325ml/');
