  ('IntexGlobal','PS4001L','Chicago Laminated Tote Bag','chicago-laminated-tote-bag-ps4001l','Bags','Tote Bags','The Chicago Laminated Tote Bag is a versatile and eye-catching accessory designed to leave a lasting impression with its full-color customization. Perfect for promotions, events, or daily use, this tote bag combines style and functionality.',1,true,false,'["Durable Material: Made from 120gsm laminated fabric, offering sturdiness and a sleek, glossy finish.", "Spacious Dimensions: Measures 29cm x 34cm, providing ample room for essentials.", "Full-Color Customization: Personalize the bag from base to handles with vibrant, full-color designs for maximum impact.", "Unique Branding Opportunity: Customize with your 29cm x 34cm image to create a distinct and memorable impression.", "Practical and Stylish: Ideal for both promotional events and everyday activities, offering durability and a polished look."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "29cm x 34cm"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Custom", "hex": "", "image": ""}]'::jsonb,null,'supplier',true,true,null,28,'indent_sea','Intex','https://www.intexglobal.com/product/chicago-laminated-tote-bag/');
