  ('IntexGlobal','PS4031','Large Non-Woven Shopping Bag','large-non-woven-shopping-bag-ps4031','Bags','Tote Bags','The Large Non-Woven Shopping Bag is designed to handle your heavier groceries with ease, offering excellent support and durability. Its spacious design and sturdy base make it a perfect choice for everyday shopping, while its customizable surface ensures your brand gets noticed.',100,true,false,'["Generous Size: Measures 33cm L x 38cm H x 24cm G, offering ample space for groceries or other essentials.", "Strong Base Support: The sturdy base inside the bag ensures it can support heavier items, making it ideal for grocery shopping.", "Durable 80gsm Non-Woven Material: Lightweight yet tough enough to handle daily use and carry heavier loads.", "Custom Branding Area: Personalize with your logo or design to make a lasting impression.", "Color Options: Available in Black, Navy, Red, Royal, and White to suit your branding or preferences."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "33cm L x 38cm H x 24cm D"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Black", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps4031/ps4031-black.webp"}, {"name": "Navy", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps4031/ps4031-navy.webp"}, {"name": "Red", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps4031/ps4031-red.webp"}, {"name": "Royal Blue", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps4031/ps4031-royal-blue.webp"}, {"name": "White", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps4031/ps4031-white.webp"}]'::jsonb,null,'supplier',true,false,null,5,'local_stock','Intex','https://www.intexglobal.com/product/large-non-woven-shopping-bag/');
