  ('IntexGlobal','PS4102','Maine Long Handle Calico Bag','maine-long-handle-calico-bag-ps4102','Bags','Cotton Tote Bags','The Maine Calico Tote is the perfect blend of sustainability and style, offering a classic design with a spacious interior and long handle for easy carrying. Ideal for retail, trade shows, or everyday use, this tote is an environmentally friendly option that promotes your brand while minimizing your ecological footprint.',100,true,false,'["Eco-Friendly 140-GSM Calico Fabric: Made from natural, sustainable material, making it a great choice for reducing environmental impact.", "Generous Size: Measures 38cm x 42cm, providing plenty of space for groceries, documents, or event materials.", "Convenient Long Handle: The 66cm long handle makes it easy to carry, whether for shopping or everyday use.", "Custom Branding Area: Personalize with a large 25cm x 25cm print area to showcase your logo or message.", "Versatile Use: Perfect for retail, trade shows, or daily activities, offering a wide range of branding opportunities."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "38cm x 42cm"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Natural", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps4102/ps4102-main.webp"}]'::jsonb,null,'supplier',true,false,null,5,'local_stock','Intex','https://www.intexglobal.com/product/maine-long-handle-calico-bag/');
