  ('IntexGlobal','PS4103','Clontarf Calico Bag','clontarf-calico-bag-ps4103','Bags','Cotton Tote Bags','The Clontarf Bag combines a timeless, practical design with ample space for your essentials. Featuring a natural color, a V-shaped gusset, and medium handles, this bag is both functional and customizable, making it a great choice for promotional events or everyday use.',100,true,false,'["Practical Design: Measures 37cm L x 42cm H with a V-shaped gusset, offering a standard yet substantial size for carrying a variety of items.", "Durable and Simple: Made from sturdy 140gsm material in a natural color, the Clontarf bag is designed to withstand regular use.", "Custom Branding Area: Features a large 25cm x 25cm print area, perfect for showcasing your logo or message.", "Versatile Use: Ideal for retail, trade shows, giveaways, or daily use, this bag offers plenty of space for promotional designs."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "37cm L x 42cm H"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Natural", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps4103/ps4103-main.webp"}]'::jsonb,null,'supplier',true,false,null,5,'local_stock','Intex','https://www.intexglobal.com/product/clontarf-calico-bag/');
