  ('IntexGlobal','PS4104','Dakota Calico Bag','dakota-calico-bag-ps4104','Bags','Cotton Tote Bags','The Dakota Calico Bag combines trendy style with functionality, making it the perfect companion for a day out or a weekend getaway. With its spacious interior, natural color, and convenient long handle, this versatile bag is ideal for trade shows, conferences, conventions, or even everyday use.',100,true,false,'["Durable 140gsm Natural Calico Fabric: Made from sturdy, eco-friendly calico, providing a sustainable choice for everyday use.", "Generous Size: Ample space for a weekend away, or to carry event materials, merchandise, or daily essentials.", "Convenient Long Handle: The long handle makes it easy and comfortable to carry, whether you''re out shopping or at a trade show.", "Custom Branding Area: The large 25cm x 25cm print area allows for easy customization to showcase your logo or promotional design.", "Versatile Use: Perfect for trade shows, conventions, retail, or even as an everyday fashion accessory."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "39cm x 42cm x 10cm"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Natural", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps4104/ps4104-main.webp"}]'::jsonb,null,'supplier',true,false,null,5,'local_stock','Intex','https://www.intexglobal.com/product/dakota-calico-bag/');
