  ('IntexGlobal','PS4106','Montana Calico Coloured Tote Bag','montana-calico-coloured-tote-bag-ps4106','Bags','Cotton Tote Bags','The Montana Calico Coloured Tote Bag offers a versatile and stylish solution for your promotional needs. With a convenient double-handled drawstring design, this tote is perfect for carrying your essentials with ease.',100,true,false,'["Durable 140gsm Calico Fabric: Made from eco-friendly, sturdy calico, providing a sustainable option for everyday use.", "Spacious Design: Measures 38cm x 40cm, offering plenty of room for your personal items, merchandise, or promotional materials.", "Double-Handed Drawstring Design: Convenient handles for easy carrying, plus a drawstring closure for added security and style.", "Custom Branding Area: The large 25cm x 25cm print area allows for easy customization, making it ideal for showcasing your logo or promotional design.", "Color Variety: Available in black, blue, natural, red, and white, allowing you to choose the perfect match for your brand."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "38cm x 40cm"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Black", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps4106/ps4106-black.webp"}, {"name": "Natural", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps4106/ps4106-natural.webp"}, {"name": "Navy", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps4106/ps4106-navy.webp"}, {"name": "Red", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps4106/ps4106-red.webp"}, {"name": "White", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps4106/ps4106-white.webp"}]'::jsonb,null,'supplier',true,false,null,5,'local_stock','Intex','https://www.intexglobal.com/product/montana-calico-col