  ('IntexGlobal','PS4108','Boston Long Handle Coloured Calico Bag','boston-long-handle-coloured-calico-bag-ps4108','Bags','Cotton Tote Bags','The Boston Long Handle Coloured Calico Bag is a versatile and practical accessory, perfect for a variety of occasions. Made from durable 130gsm calico fabric, it is available in a range of vibrant colours, making it an excellent choice for your promotional needs.',100,true,false,'["Eco-Friendly and Durable: Crafted from 130gsm calico fabric, this bag is reusable and environmentally friendly, offering a sustainable option for your brand.", "Spacious Design: Measuring 38cm x 40cm, it provides ample space for your essentials, from groceries to promotional materials.", "Long Sling Handle: The long handle design makes it comfortable to carry, perfect for daily use, travel, or trade shows.", "Custom Branding Area: The large 25cm x 25cm print area allows you to showcase your logo, artwork, or promotional message.", "Color Variety: Available in black, blue, red, green, navy, and white, giving you the flexibility to match your brand''s color scheme."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "38cm x 40cm"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Black", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps4108/ps4108-black.webp"}, {"name": "Green", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps4108/ps4108-green.webp"}, {"name": "Navy", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps4108/ps4108-navy.webp"}, {"name": "Red", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps4108/ps4108-red.webp"}, {"name": "Royal Blue", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps4108/ps4108-royal-blue.webp"}]'::jsonb,null,'supplier',true,false,null,