  ('IntexGlobal','PS4113','Cotton Tote Bag','cotton-tote-bag-ps4113','Bags','Cotton Tote Bags','The Cotton Tote Bag is the perfect balance of simplicity, style, and functionality. Crafted from natural-toned cotton, this tote bag features a generous volume with a 9cm gusset and short handles.',100,true,false,'["Durable and Eco-Friendly: Made from high-quality 140gsm cotton, this bag is both sturdy and sustainable, offering an eco-friendly option for daily use.", "Generous Customization Area: The large surface area allows for a 25cm x 25cm print, making it easy to display your brand''s message or artwork.", "Spacious Design: With a size of 42cm x 37cm and a 9cm gusset, the bag offers ample space for carrying books, shopping items, or event materials.", "Stylish and Simple: The natural cotton color gives the bag a trendy, minimalist look, ideal for any occasion.", "Perfect for Events: Ideal for tradeshows, conventions, retail stores, and giveaways, ensuring your brand is seen wherever the bag goes."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "37cm W x 42cm H x 9cm Gusset"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Natural", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps4113/ps4113-main.webp"}]'::jsonb,null,'supplier',true,false,null,5,'local_stock','Intex','https://www.intexglobal.com/product/cotton-tote-bag/');
