  ('IntexGlobal','PS4202C','Minnesota Canvas Coloured Tote Bag','minnesota-canvas-coloured-tote-bag-ps4202c','Bags','Tote Bags','The Minnesota Canvas Colour Tote Bag combines eco-friendly materials with a variety of vibrant colors, offering both practicality and style. With a generous print area, it''s perfect for showcasing your brand or artwork.',100,true,false,'["Eco-Friendly and Durable: Crafted from 320gsm canvas, this tote bag is a reusable and sustainable choice, ideal for those looking to reduce their environmental impact.", "Customizable Design: With a 25cm x 25cm print area, you can easily personalize the tote with your logo, artwork, or promotional message for maximum visibility.", "Spacious and Practical: At 38cm x 42cm, this tote offers ample room for groceries, books, or merchandise.", "Comfortable to Carry: The double long handles provide comfort and support, even with heavier items.", "Available in Multiple Colours: Choose from black, red, navy, charcoal, or sage to match your branding or personal style.", "Perfect for Promotions: Ideal for trade shows, retail, or any event, ensuring your brand makes a lasting impression."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "38cm x 42cm"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Black", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps4202c/ps4202c-black.webp"}, {"name": "Camel", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps4202c/ps4202c-camel.webp"}, {"name": "Charcoal", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps4202c/ps4202c-charcoal.webp"}, {"name": "Navy", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps4202c/ps4202c-navy.webp"}, {"name": "Olive", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/p