  ('IntexGlobal','PS4209','Bondi Canvas Tote Bag - Natural','bondi-canvas-tote-bag-natural-ps4209','Bags','Tote Bags','The Bondi Canvas Tote Bag is the perfect blend of style, functionality, and durability. Designed with a spacious interior and beach-inspired style, this extra-large canvas bag is ideal for everything from beach trips to retail shopping and everyday outings. Made from 100% high-quality canvas.',100,true,false,'["Generous Size: Measures 42cm (W) x 23cm (H) x 36cm (gusset), providing a spacious interior for all your items.", "Durable Material: Crafted from 280gsm 100% canvas material for strength and reliability.", "Multiple Pockets: Equipped with internal and external pockets, plus an internal zipper pocket, ensuring secure storage for smaller items like keys, wallets, or phones.", "Long Handles: The convenient long handles make it easy to carry over your shoulder, adding to its comfort and practicality.", "Perfect for Customization: Ideal for screen printing or full-color transfers, with a large print area to showcase your unique designs, logos, or artwork."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "42cm(w) x 36(h) x 23(gusset)"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Natural", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps4209/ps4209-main.webp"}]'::jsonb,null,'supplier',true,false,null,5,'local_stock','Intex','https://www.intexglobal.com/product/bondi-canvas-tote-bag-natural/');
