  ('IntexGlobal','PS4305','20 Litre Non Woven Cooler Bag','20-litre-non-woven-cooler-bag-ps4305','Bags','Cooler Bags','Introducing the 20 Litre Non-Woven Cooler Bag, the perfect companion for your trips to the beach, picnics, BBQs, and grocery runs. Crafted from durable 90gsm new polypropylene material.',100,true,false,'["Size & Capacity: Measures 31cm (W) x 32cm (H) x 21cm (L), offering a 20-litre capacity to store groceries, snacks, and drinks.", "Durable Construction: Made from high-quality 90gsm polypropylene, ensuring the bag can handle heavy products.", "Temperature Control: Equipped with aluminium foil PE foam insulation to keep your groceries cool for longer.", "Versatile Design: Perfect for the beach, picnics, BBQs, and grocery shopping, making it a versatile option for various activities.", "Secure Zip Closure: Keeps your items protected and at the right temperature.", "Customizable: With a 14cm x 14cm print area, customization is easy for adding your personal or brand logo."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "31cm W x 32cm H x 21cm L"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Black", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps4305/ps4305-black.webp"}, {"name": "Green", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps4305/ps4305-green.webp"}, {"name": "Light Blue", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps4305/ps4305-light-blue.webp"}, {"name": "Navy", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps4305/ps4305-navy.webp"}, {"name": "Orange", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps4305/ps4305-orange.webp"}, {"name": "Red", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_var