  ('IntexGlobal','PS4306','Budget Cooler Bag Nylon','budget-cooler-bag-nylon-ps4306','Bags','Cooler Bags','The Budget Cooler Bag Nylon is the ideal compact solution for keeping your food and drinks cool during weekends away, BBQs, or picnics. Made from durable 210D polyester, this 4.2L cooler bag features aluminium foil laminated PE foam insulation to ensure your items stay at the perfect temperature.',100,true,false,'["Compact Size: Measures 20cm (W) x 15cm (H) x 15cm (L) with a 4.2L capacity, perfect for storing snacks and drinks.", "Durable Material: Manufactured from 210D polyester for strength and durability.", "Temperature Control: Aluminium foil laminated PE foam keeps your food and beverages cool for longer.", "Practical Design: Equipped with a zipped top for secure closure and a front slip pocket for easy access.", "Convenient Carry Handle: A woven handle makes it easy to transport the cooler bag on your trips.", "Customizable: Customization is easy with a 12cm x 6cm print area, perfect for your personal or company branding."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "20cm W x 15cm H x 15cm L"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Black", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps4306/ps4306-black.webp"}, {"name": "Green", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps4306/ps4306-green.webp"}, {"name": "Light Blue", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps4306/ps4306-light-blue.webp"}, {"name": "Navy", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps4306/ps4306-navy.webp"}, {"name": "Orange", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps4306/ps4306-orange.webp"}, {"name": "Red", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab9