  ('IntexGlobal','PS4310','Budget Cooler Bag With Grip','budget-cooler-bag-with-grip-ps4310','Bags','Cooler Bags','The Budget Cooler Bag with Grip is a practical and stylish solution to keep your food and drinks cool all day long. Made from durable 210D polyester, this 3.5L cooler bag features aluminium foil laminated PE foam insulation, perfect for keeping your lunch or drinks at the right temperature. The woven carry handle offers comfort, and the velcro top closure along with the external slip pocket adds c',100,true,false,'["Compact and Convenient: Measures 17.5cm (W) x 24cm (H) x 12.5cm (L) with a 3.5L capacity, ideal for carrying lunch or small items.", "Durable Material: Crafted from 210D polyester for lasting strength and wear resistance.", "Effective Insulation: Aluminium foil laminated PE foam keeps your food and beverages cool for hours.", "Easy Access: Features a velcro top closure for quick opening and closing, with an external slip pocket for added convenience.", "Comfortable Carrying: Woven carry handle ensures easy and comfortable handling.", "Customizable: Customization is simple with a 12cm x 6cm print area, perfect for adding your brand logo or personal design."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "17.5cm W x 24cm H x 12.5cm L"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Black", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps4310/ps4310-black.webp"}, {"name": "Green", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps4310/ps4310-green.webp"}, {"name": "Light Blue", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps4310/ps4310-light-blue.webp"}, {"name": "Navy", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps4310/ps4310-navy.webp"}, {"name": "Orange", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413