  ('IntexGlobal','PS4351','25L Cooler Box Camping & Outdoor','25l-cooler-box-camping-outdoor-ps4351','Outdoor & Lifestyle','Camping & Outdoors','The 25L BELL Cooler Box is your go-to solution for keeping beverages chilled for extended periods, whether for outdoor adventures or events. Combining functionality with a rugged design, it’s built to last and impress. Note: Cooler boxes do not fall under Free Freight. Please contact us for a quote!',5,true,false,'["Tough Rotomolded LLDPE Construction: Engineered for durability with a thick PU foam layer to maintain optimal insulation.", "UV-Resistant Colours: Ensures the cooler remains vibrant and fade-free, even under harsh sunlight.", "Generous Capacity: Holds up to 30 standard 375ml cans with ice on top, perfect for group gatherings.", "Convenient Features: Includes a sturdy rope handle with a comfortable rubber grip and a side tap for easy drainage of excess water.", "Superior Insulation: Keeps contents cold for an impressive 3-5 Days.", "Customizable Branding: Available unbranded or with a full-colour vinyl decal for maximum brand visibility (confirm artwork suitability for size restrictions)."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "46.3cm W x 35.2cm H x 33.6 cm D"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Mountain Blue", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps4351/ps4351-mountain-blue.webp"}, {"name": "Tan", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps4351/ps4351-tan.webp"}, {"name": "White", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps4351/ps4351-white.webp"}]'::jsonb,null,'supplier',true,false,null,5,'local_stock','Intex','https://www.intexglobal.com/product/25l-cooler-box/');
