  ('IntexGlobal','PS4352','31L Cooler Box with Wheels Camping & Outdoor','31l-cooler-box-with-wheels-camping-outdoor-ps4352','Outdoor & Lifestyle','Camping & Outdoors','The 31L BELL Cooler Box with Wheels combines robust construction, excellent insulation, and practical features, making it the perfect solution for keeping beverages cold on the go. Note: Cooler boxes do not fall under Free Freight. Please contact us for a quote!',5,true,false,'["Durable Rotomolded LDPE Build: Crafted with a tough exterior and a thick PU foam layer for superior insulation.", "UV-Resistant Colours: Stays vibrant and fade-free even in extreme sunlight.", "Enhanced Mobility: Features a strong telescopic handle and rugged wheels, perfect for navigating all terrains.", "Built-In Convenience: Equipped with a built-in bottle opener and a lid that doubles as a seat with two integrated cup holders.", "Generous Capacity: Holds up to 44 standard 375ml cans with ice on top.", "Efficient Drainage: Includes a side tap for draining excess water with ease.", "Exceptional Insulation: Keeps contents cold for 3-5 Days, ensuring your refreshments are always ready.", "Customizable Branding: Available unbranded or with a full-colour vinyl decal (Confirm artwork suitability for size restrictions)."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "53.6cm W x 47.5cm H x 38.2cm D"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Mountain Blue", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps4352/ps4352-mountain-blue.webp"}, {"name": "Tan", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps4352/ps4352-tan.webp"}, {"name": "White", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps4352/ps4352-white.webp"}]'::jsonb,null,'supplier',true,false,null,5,'local_stock','Intex','https://www.intexglobal.com/product/31l-cooler-box-with-wheels/');
