  ('IntexGlobal','PS4353','31L Cooler Box Camping & Outdoor','31l-cooler-box-camping-outdoor-ps4353','Outdoor & Lifestyle','Camping & Outdoors','The 31L BELL Cooler Box is engineered for superior beverage chilling, offering durability and functionality for all your outdoor adventures. Note: Cooler boxes do not fall under Free Freight. Please contact us for a quote!',5,true,false,'["Rugged Rotomolded Construction: Made from tough low-density PE with a thick PU foam layer for maximum insulation.", "UV-Resistant Colours: Keeps its vibrant appearance without fading, even in direct sunlight.", "Convenient Rope Handle: Equipped with a sturdy rope handle featuring a comfortable rubber grip for easy transport.", "Built-In Bottle Opener: Integrated within the rubber lock for easy access.", "Ample Capacity: Holds up to 36 standard 375ml cans with ice on top.", "Efficient Water Drainage: Side tap allows for quick removal of melted ice water.", "Long-Lasting Insulation: Designed to keep contents cold for 3-5 WORKING DAYS.", "Custom Branding Options: Available unbranded or with a vibrant full-colour vinyl decal (confirm artwork size suitability)."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "61cm W x 40cm H x 38cm D"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "White", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps4353/ps4353-main.webp"}]'::jsonb,null,'supplier',true,false,null,5,'local_stock','Intex','https://www.intexglobal.com/product/31l-cooler-box/');
