  ('IntexGlobal','PS4355','11L Premium Cooler Box Camping & Outdoor','11l-premium-cooler-box-camping-outdoor-ps4355','Outdoor & Lifestyle','Camping & Outdoors','Introducing 11L Premium Cooler Box with Bamboo Lid, perfect for picnics, BBQs, and casual gatherings. This cooler combines modern aesthetics with functional design to keep your beverages chilled while enhancing your event setup. Note: Cooler boxes do not fall under Free Freight. Please contact us for a quote!',5,true,false,'["Durable Bamboo Lid: Adds a touch of elegance and doubles as a flat surface for convenience.", "Eco-Friendly Body: Crafted from food-grade, non-toxic PP material, ensuring safety and sustainability.", "Ample Capacity: Holds up to 14 standard cans with room for ice on top.", "Customizable Front Panel: Ideal for branding via a sticker decoration.", "Portable and Practical: Lightweight and compact design for easy transport and storage."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "34.5cm W x 24cm H x 23cm D"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "White", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps4355/ps4355-main.webp"}]'::jsonb,null,'supplier',true,false,null,5,'local_stock','Intex','https://www.intexglobal.com/product/11l-premium-cooler-box/');
