  ('IntexGlobal','PS4356','Paradise 12L Cooler Box Camping & Outdoor','paradise-12l-cooler-box-camping-outdoor-ps4356','Outdoor & Lifestyle','Camping & Outdoors','Meet the New Paradise 12L Cooler Box – where style meets functionality for all your outdoor adventures. Whether you''re heading to the beach, planning a picnic, or enjoying a road trip, this sleek and insulated cooler keeps your food and drinks fresh for hours while adding a touch of elegance to your travels. Note: Cooler boxes do not fall under Free Freight. Please contact us for a quote!',5,true,false,'["Insulated & Leak-Proof – Keeps contents chilled and prevents messy leaks.", "Spacious 12L Capacity – Roomy enough for all your favorite snacks and beverages.", "Detachable Insulated Lid – Easy access and effortless cleaning.", "Stylish PU Tan Strap – Designed with chic gold buckles for a premium look.", "Lightweight & Portable – Convenience without compromising on storage."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "33cm L x 21cm W x 23cm H"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Black", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps4356/ps4356-black.webp"}, {"name": "Blue", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps4356/ps4356-blue.webp"}, {"name": "White", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps4356/ps4356-white.webp"}]'::jsonb,null,'supplier',true,false,null,5,'local_stock','Intex','https://www.intexglobal.com/product/paradise-12l-cooler-box/');
