  ('IntexGlobal','PS4401','Nylon Drawstring Bag','nylon-drawstring-bag-ps4401','Bags','Drawstring Bags','The Nylon Drawstring Bag is the perfect companion for your active lifestyle. Made from water-repellent 210D nylon, it keeps your belongings dry even on rainy days.',100,true,false,'["Water-Repellent Material: Crafted from 210D nylon, this bag keeps your items dry, even on rainy days.", "Spacious Design: Measures 39cm x 49cm, providing ample space for your gym clothes, sports gear, or daily essentials.", "Secure Closure: Features rope handles that help keep your items safely contained.", "Customizable: Add your unique design or logo with an 18cm x 18cm print area for a personal touch.", "Variety of Colours: Available in black, navy, orange, red, royal, white, and yellow to suit your style and branding needs."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "39cm(w) x 49cm(h)"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Blue", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps4401/ps4401-blue.webp"}, {"name": "Navy", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps4401/ps4401-navy.webp"}, {"name": "Orange", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps4401/ps4401-orange.webp"}, {"name": "Red", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps4401/ps4401-red.webp"}, {"name": "White", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps4401/ps4401-white.webp"}, {"name": "Yellow", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps4401/ps4401-yellow.webp"}, {"name": "Royal", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps4401/ps4401-royal.webp"}]'::jsonb,null,'supplier',true,false,null,5,'local_stock','Intex','https://www.intexglobal.com/product/nylon-drawstring-bag/');
