  ('IntexGlobal','PS4510','Laminated Jute Beach Bag With Cotton Handles And Front Pocket','laminated-jute-beach-bag-with-cotton-handles-and-front-pocket-ps4510','Bags','Jute Bags','This Laminated Jute Beach Bag is the perfect combination of style, durability, and eco-friendliness. Crafted from 100% hessian, this spacious bag features cotton handles and a convenient front pocket, making it ideal for beach trips, shopping, or daily use.',100,true,false,'["Dimensions: 44.5 cm x 35 cm x 15 cm, offering ample space to carry beach essentials, groceries, or personal items.", "Material: Made from 100% hessian (jute), a sturdy and eco-friendly material, laminated for added durability and easy maintenance.", "Customisation: Large 35cm x 15cm print area, perfect for showcasing your logo, artwork, or promotional designs for a lasting impression.", "Front Pocket: Convenient pocket for easy storage of smaller items such as keys, phone, or sunscreen.", "Cotton Handles: Comfortable, sturdy cotton handles for easy carrying, making it ideal for trips to the beach, shopping, or travel.", "Colour Variety: Available in a range of colours to suit your brand or personal preferences."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "44.5 cm x 35 cm x 15 cm"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Natural", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps4510/ps4510-main.webp"}]'::jsonb,null,'supplier',true,false,null,5,'local_stock','Intex','https://www.intexglobal.com/product/laminated-jute-beach-bag-with-cotton-handles-and-front-pocket/');
