  ('IntexGlobal','PS4513','Hemp Tote Bag without Gusset','hemp-tote-bag-without-gusset-ps4513','Bags','Cotton Tote Bags','Introducing the Hemp Tote Bag—a perfect blend of style, sustainability, and practicality. Crafted from 100% organic hemp fibers, this eco-friendly tote is not only durable but also a versatile companion for all your adventures.',100,true,false,'["Dimensions: 38 cm (W) x 41 cm (H) — a spacious, simple design ideal for everyday use, shopping, or as a promotional item.", "Material: Made from 100% organic 140gsm hemp fibers, known for their durability, natural feel, and environmental benefits.", "Eco-Friendly: A sustainable choice that reduces the use of synthetic materials, contributing to a greener planet.", "Customisation: The large print area offers ample space for your design or logo, perfect for creating a unique and lasting impression.", "Versatile Use: Great for retail, trade shows, conventions, or everyday use, offering both functionality and style."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "38(w) x 41(h) cm"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Natural", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps4513/ps4513-main.webp"}]'::jsonb,null,'supplier',true,false,null,5,'local_stock','Intex','https://www.intexglobal.com/product/hemp-tote-bag-without-gusset/');
