  ('IntexGlobal','PS4601LS','Kraft Paper Bag Brown Landscape Includes Twisted Paper Handle','kraft-paper-bag-brown-landscape-includes-twisted-paper-handle-ps4601ls','Bags','Paper Bags','Introducing the Kraft Paper Bag Brown Landscape with Twisted Paper Handle—a sustainable and functional solution for retail, trade shows, and promotional events. This eco-friendly paper bag offers ample space for a variety of items while maintaining an elegant, natural look.',100,true,false,'["Dimensions: 42 cm (W) x 31 cm (H) x 11 cm (G)— providing generous space for retail products, gifts, or promotional materials in a landscape orientation.", "Material: Made from 130gsm eco-friendly kraft paper, this bag is biodegradable and a more sustainable alternative to plastic bags.", "Twisted Paper Handles: Durable twisted paper handles ensure a strong and comfortable grip for customers, making it perfect for carrying heavier items.", "Customisation: With a print area of 13 cm (W) x 25 cm (H), you can easily personalise the bag with your logo, message, or artwork to create a lasting impression.", "Colour: Available in a natural brown kraft paper colour, offering a simple, rustic, and environmentally conscious aesthetic."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "42cm W x 31 cm H x 11cm G"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Kraft", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps4601ls/ps4601ls-kraft.webp"}]'::jsonb,null,'supplier',true,false,null,5,'local_stock','Intex','https://www.intexglobal.com/product/kraft-paper-bag-brown-landscape-includes-twisted-paper-handle/');
