  ('IntexGlobal','PS4601M','Kraft Paper Bag Brown Medium Includes Twisted Paper Handle','kraft-paper-bag-brown-medium-includes-twisted-paper-handle-ps4601m','Bags','Paper Bags','Introducing the Kraft Paper Bag Brown Medium with Twisted Paper Handle—an eco-friendly and stylish packaging solution for retail, events, and promotional purposes. This medium-sized kraft paper bag is perfect for carrying a variety of products while promoting your brand with a natural and sustainable touch.',100,true,false,'["Dimensions: 26 cm (W) x 35 cm (H) x 9 cm (G) — offering the perfect size for medium-sized retail items, gifts, or giveaways", "Material: Made from 130gsm eco-friendly kraft paper, this bag is a biodegradable, recyclable, and sustainable option for businesses", "Twisted Paper Handles: Featuring durable twisted paper handles for added strength and a comfortable grip, making it ideal for carrying heavier items", "Customisation: The 9 cm (W) x 15 cm (H) print area allows you to personalise the bag with your logo, artwork, or message for a unique promotional tool", "Colour: Available in a natural brown kraft paper colour, providing a rustic, environmentally conscious look."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "26 cm W x 35 cm H x 9 cm G"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Kraft", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps4601m/ps4601m-kraft.webp"}]'::jsonb,null,'supplier',true,false,null,5,'local_stock','Intex','https://www.intexglobal.com/product/kraft-paper-bag-brown-medium-includes-twisted-paper-handle/');
