  ('IntexGlobal','PS4601S','Kraft Paper Bag Brown Small Includes Twisted Paper Handle','kraft-paper-bag-brown-small-includes-twisted-paper-handle-ps4601s','Bags','Paper Bags','Introducing the Kraft Paper Bag Brown Small with Twisted Paper Handle—a compact and eco-friendly packaging solution for your retail and promotional needs. This small kraft paper bag offers durability and style, perfect for packaging smaller products, gifts, or samples.',100,true,false,'["Dimensions: 20 cm (W) x 29 cm (H) x 10 cm (G) — ideal for smaller items, such as cosmetics, accessories, or gifts.", "Material: Made from 130gsm eco-friendly kraft paper, this bag is both biodegradable and recyclable, offering an environmentally conscious alternative to plastic bags.", "Twisted Paper Handles: The bag features durable twisted paper handles, providing strength and ensuring a secure grip while carrying.", "Customisation: Customise the bag with your logo, artwork, or design using the 9 cm (W) x 13 cm (H) print area, creating a unique promotional item.", "Colour Options: Available in natural brown and offering versatility for various branding styles."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "20cm W x 29cm H x 10cm G"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Brown", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps4601s/ps4601s-main.webp"}]'::jsonb,null,'supplier',true,false,null,5,'local_stock','Intex','https://www.intexglobal.com/product/kraft-paper-bag-brown-small-includes-twisted-paper-handle/');
