  ('IntexGlobal','PS4701','Rpet Felt Tote Bag','rpet-felt-tote-bag-ps4701','Bags','Tote Bags','The RPET Felt Tote Bag is the perfect blend of sustainability, style, and practicality. Made from 1mm RPET felt, this eco-friendly tote bag offers a durable solution for your everyday carrying needs.',100,true,false,'["Dimensions: The tote measures 36 cm (W) x 40 cm (H), with 60 cm long handles, providing ample space for carrying essentials while ensuring comfortable shoulder straps for easy use.", "Material: Crafted from 1mm RPET felt, this bag is made from recycled PET plastic bottles, offering a sustainable alternative to traditional fabric bags and contributing to a reduction in plastic waste.", "Durable Handles: The tote features long handles made from polyester webbing, providing extra strength and comfort, even when carrying heavier items.", "Eco-Friendly: As an RPET product, this bag supports environmental sustainability by utilizing recycled materials, helping reduce plastic waste.", "Customisation: The smooth felt surface makes it an excellent canvas for custom designs, making it perfect for branding or promotional use. Add your logo or message for a unique and impactful impression.", "Versatile Use: Ideal for everyday activities like shopping, commuting, or attending events, the bag is both practical and stylish."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "36 x 40 cm  (Handle - 60cm)"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Grey", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps4701/ps4701-main.webp"}]'::jsonb,null,'supplier',true,false,null,5,'local_stock','Intex','https://www.intexglobal.com/product/rpet-felt-tote-bag/');
