  ('IntexGlobal','PS500X249','Plush Terry Sport Headband Sport Product','plush-terry-sport-headband-sport-product-ps500x249','Outdoor & Lifestyle','Sports Products','Introducing Plush Terry Sport Headband, a must-have accessory for active lifestyles. Designed to combine comfort and practicality, it ensures you stay focused on your fitness goals.',250,true,false,'["Plush Terry Fabric: Provides exceptional softness against the skin and superior moisture-wicking properties to keep you dry.", "Sweat Absorption: Effectively absorbs sweat, allowing you to stay comfortable during intense workouts.", "Stay-in-Place Design: Keeps hair out of your face, helping you concentrate on your activity.", "Versatile Use: Perfect for a variety of activities, including workouts, sports, and outdoor adventures."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "19cm L x 5cm H"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Black", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps500x249/ps500x249-black.webp"}, {"name": "Blue", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps500x249/ps500x249-blue.webp"}, {"name": "Orange", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps500x249/ps500x249-orange.webp"}, {"name": "Pink", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps500x249/ps500x249-pink.webp"}, {"name": "Red", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps500x249/ps500x249-red.webp"}, {"name": "White", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps500x249/ps500x249-white.webp"}]'::jsonb,null,'supplier',true,true,0.86,28,'indent_sea','Intex','https://www.intexglobal.com/product/plush-terry-sport-headband/');
