  ('IntexGlobal','PS5100','Snazzy Crew Jacquard Socks','snazzy-crew-jacquard-socks-ps5100','Apparel','Socks','Our Snazzy Crew Jacquard Socks are the perfect blend of style, comfort, and functionality, making them ideal for any occasion—from casual outings to formal events.',1,true,false,'["Premium Material: Crafted from 80% cotton, 17% polyester, and 3% spandex for a soft, breathable, and flexible fit", "Lightweight Compression: Provides gentle support, making these socks suitable for everyday wear and sports activities", "Eye-Catching Jacquard Embroidery: Highlight your unique designs with intricate and vibrant patterns", "Customizable for Branding: Personalized designs enhance brand visibility and promotional impact", "Versatile and Comfortable: Perfect for complementing any outfit while offering all-day comfort."]'::jsonb,'[]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Custom", "hex": "", "image": ""}]'::jsonb,null,'supplier',true,true,null,28,'indent_sea','Intex','https://www.intexglobal.com/product/crew-jacquard-socks/');
