  ('IntexGlobal','PS5303','Whipbird Bamboo Usb Flash Drive','whipbird-bamboo-usb-flash-drive-ps5303','Tech','USB Flash Drives','The Whipbird Bamboo USB Flash Drive combines sustainability and functionality, offering a unique and eco-conscious solution for your data storage needs. Note : USB prices change frequently. Please contact our sales team for the latest price quote.',1,true,false,'["Natural Bamboo Construction: Made from sustainable bamboo, providing a sleek and environmentally friendly alternative to traditional USB drives.", "Compact and Portable: Lightweight design makes it easy to carry and use on the go.", "Customizable Surface: Perfect for engraving or printing logos, making it a standout promotional item or personalized gift.", "Versatile Use: Ideal for work, school, or personal file storage and transfer.", "Eco-Friendly Appeal: An excellent choice for businesses or individuals looking to reduce their environmental footprint."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "5.7cm x 1.9cm"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Brown", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps5303/ps5303-main.webp"}]'::jsonb,null,'supplier',true,true,null,28,'indent_sea','Intex','https://www.intexglobal.com/product/whipbird-bamboo-usb-flash-drive/');
