  ('IntexGlobal','PS6011','PVC Pocket Landscape Lanyard','pvc-pocket-landscape-lanyard-ps6011','Promotional Giveaways','Lanyards','Introducing the PVC Pocket Landscape – a clear, transparent pocket designed to showcase your printed materials in a neat and professional manner. This pocket is ideal for displaying business cards, photos, or promotional items in a compact and durable format.',100,true,false,'["Clear Transparent PVC: Offers a crystal-clear view of your printed materials for easy readability", "Custom Print Size: Perfect for prints up to 9.2 cm (W) x 6 cm (H), ideal for business cards or small documents", "Durable Construction: Made from sturdy PVC for long-lasting protection", "Compact & Convenient: Fits easily in lanyards for on-the-go use."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "10 x 8 cm"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Clear", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps6011/ps6011-main.webp"}]'::jsonb,null,'supplier',true,false,null,12,'local_stock','Intex','https://www.intexglobal.com/product/pvc-pocket-landscape/');
