  ('IntexGlobal','PS6012','PVC Pocket Portrait Lanyard','pvc-pocket-portrait-lanyard-ps6012','Promotional Giveaways','Lanyards','Introducing the PVC Pocket Portrait – a clear, transparent pocket designed to display your printed materials in a compact and professional way. Perfect for showcasing ID cards, business cards, or small promotional items, this pocket offers durability and versatility.',100,true,false,'["Clear Transparent PVC: Provides a clear view of your printed materials for easy visibility", "Custom Print Size: Ideal for prints up to 6 cm (W) x 10 cm (H), perfect for business cards or small graphics", "Durable Construction: Made from strong PVC for long-lasting use", "Compact and Convenient: Fits easily in lanyards for on-the-go display."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "6.4 x 11 cm"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Clear", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps6012/ps6012-main.webp"}]'::jsonb,null,'supplier',true,false,null,12,'local_stock','Intex','https://www.intexglobal.com/product/pvc-pocket-portrait/');
