  ('IntexGlobal','PS7011','Premium Hard Cover Notebook - A5','premium-hard-cover-notebook-a5-ps7011','Office & Desk','Notebooks','The A5 Premium Hard Cover Notebook is the perfect blend of style and functionality, designed to meet the needs of professionals, students, and creatives.',100,true,false,'["PU Leather-Lined Hard Cover: Offers a sophisticated and durable finish for a professional appearance.", "240 Lined Pages: 120 high-quality leaves provide ample space for notes, journaling, or planning.", "Made with recycled paper for an environmentally friendly choice.", "Matching Elastic Strap: Keeps the notebook securely closed and adds a cohesive, stylish touch.", "Customizable Design: Ideal for digital printing or debossing to showcase your brand or message.", "A5 Size: Compact and portable, perfect for daily use at work, school, or travel."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "14.7 x 21 x 1.2 cm"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Black", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps7011/ps7011-main.webp"}]'::jsonb,null,'supplier',true,false,null,5,'local_stock','Intex','https://www.intexglobal.com/product/premium-hard-cover-notebook-a5/');
