  ('IntexGlobal','PS8120','Slap Can Stubby Coolers Stubby Holder','slap-can-stubby-coolers-stubby-holder-ps8120','Barware','Stubby Holders','The Slap Can Stubby Cooler is a unique and practical accessory, perfect for keeping your drinks cold while adding a playful twist. Its versatile design makes it ideal for various uses and occasions.',1,true,false,'["Durable Neoprene Blend: Ensures excellent insulation to keep beverages cooler for longer.", "Full-Color Sublimation: Fully customizable with vibrant, high-quality designs for maximum branding or personalization.", "Versatile Fit: Designed to wrap securely around cans, bottles, glasses, wrists, and more.", "Portable and Fun Design: Slap it on for a snug fit and easy removal, perfect for events, parties, or promotions."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "23cmW x 9cmH"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Black", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps8120/ps8120-black.webp"}, {"name": "White", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps8120/ps8120-white.webp"}]'::jsonb,null,'supplier',true,true,null,28,'indent_sea','Intex','https://www.intexglobal.com/product/slap-can-stubby-coolers/');
