  ('IntexGlobal','PS8501','Cooling Towel Large','cooling-towel-large-ps8501','Outdoor & Lifestyle','Towels','Introducing our Cooling Towel Large, the perfect solution to beat the heat during your most intense activities. Made from a durable nylon and polyester blend, this towel offers immediate cooling relief with just a simple wet and wring action.',250,true,false,'["Instant Cooling: Simply wet and wring out to activate the cooling effect, helping you stay comfortable during hot days or intense workouts.", "160gsm Material: Lightweight yet durable, offering optimal cooling performance without compromising comfort.", "Generous Size: Measuring 100cm W x 30cm H, it provides ample coverage for your neck, shoulders, or larger areas of your body.", "Durable Nylon and Polyester Blend: Crafted for strength and flexibility, ensuring long-lasting use and reliability.", "Portable and Lightweight: Easy to carry and store, ideal for sports, fitness routines, outdoor adventures, or everyday use."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "100cm W x 30cm H"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Black", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps8501/ps8501-black.webp"}, {"name": "Green", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps8501/ps8501-green.webp"}, {"name": "Grey", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps8501/ps8501-grey.webp"}, {"name": "Light Blue", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps8501/ps8501-light-blue.webp"}, {"name": "Navy", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps8501/ps8501-navy.webp"}, {"name": "Orange", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/