  ('IntexGlobal','PS8503','Cooling Towel Medium','cooling-towel-medium-ps8503','Outdoor & Lifestyle','Towels','Introducing our Cooling Towel Medium, designed to keep you refreshed and comfortable during any activity. Made from a high-performance nylon and polyester blend, this towel offers a quick and effective cooling solution when you need it most.',250,true,false,'["Cooling Effect: Simply wet and wring out to activate the cooling technology, providing instant relief on hot days or after workouts.", "Perfect Size: Measuring 80cm W x 30cm H, it offers ample coverage for the neck, face, or body.", "Durable Nylon and Polyester Blend: Crafted from a blend of nylon and polyester for strength, flexibility, and long-lasting use.", "160gsm Material: Lightweight yet durable, offering optimal cooling performance without compromising comfort.", "Lightweight and Compact: Easy to carry, making it perfect for sports, fitness routines, outdoor activities, or even just relaxing in the heat."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "80cm W x 30cm H"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Black", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps8503/ps8503-black.webp"}, {"name": "Green", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps8503/ps8503-green.webp"}, {"name": "Grey", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps8503/ps8503-grey.webp"}, {"name": "Light Blue", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps8503/ps8503-light-blue.webp"}, {"name": "Navy", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps8503/ps8503-navy.webp"}, {"name": "Orange", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps8503/