  ('IntexGlobal','PS9111','Sublimated Sunglasses Strap','sublimated-sunglasses-strap-ps9111','Outdoor & Lifestyle','Sunglasses','Introducing the Sublimated Sunglasses Strap, crafted from durable neoprene material for maximum flexibility and comfort. This strap is the perfect solution to keep your sunglasses secure and easily accessible, ensuring they won''t fall or get lost while you''re on the move.',250,true,false,'["Durable Neoprene Material: Flexible and comfortable, designed to last while offering a soft touch around your neck.", "Secure Fit: Holds your sunglasses firmly in place, preventing them from slipping or getting misplaced.", "Customizable Design: Features sublimation decoration, allowing vibrant, full-color, intricate designs to be printed all over the strap.", "Stylish Accessory: A functional yet fashionable way to personalize your sunglasses experience."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "2(w) x 42(h) cm"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Black", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps9111/ps9111-black.webp"}, {"name": "Blue", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps9111/ps9111-blue.webp"}, {"name": "Green", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps9111/ps9111-green.webp"}, {"name": "Orange", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps9111/ps9111-orange.webp"}, {"name": "Red", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps9111/ps9111-red.webp"}]'::jsonb,null,'supplier',true,true,0.7,28,'indent_sea','Intex','https://www.intexglobal.com/product/sublimated-sunglasses-strap/');
