  ('IntexGlobal','PS9122','Reusable Steel Straw Set - Natural Drink Bottle','reusable-steel-straw-set-natural-drink-bottle-ps9122','Drinkware','Drink Bottles','Introducing Reusable Steel Straw Set, designed to reduce plastic waste while offering a stylish and practical solution for your beverages. Packed in a natural calico pouch, this set includes everything you need for a cleaner, greener drinking experience.',50,true,false,'["Stainless Steel Straw Set: Includes 1 straight straw, 1 bent straw, and 1 cleaning brush for easy maintenance.", "Eco-Friendly Calico Pouch: A natural, reusable pouch for convenient storage and on-the-go use.", "Customizable Pouch: Decoration via print on the pouch, perfect for branding or personalizing as a gift.", "Dishwasher Safe: Easy to clean and maintain, ensuring long-term use without hassle."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "Pouch: 26 x 7.5 cm, Straw: 0.6 x 21.5 cm"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Natural", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps9122/ps9122-main.webp"}]'::jsonb,null,'supplier',true,false,null,5,'local_stock','Intex','https://www.intexglobal.com/product/reusable-steel-straw-set-natural/');
