  ('IntexGlobal','PSSUN02','30Ml Spf50 Sunscreen Lotion With Carabiner','30ml-spf50-sunscreen-lotion-with-carabiner-pssun02','Personal Care','Sunscreen & Lotions','Introducing the 30ml SPF50 Sunscreen Lotion with Carabiner by Sunsational – a portable and effective sun protection solution for all your outdoor adventures.',100,true,false,'["SPF50+ Broad Spectrum Protection: Shields against both UVA and UVB rays, ensuring superior sun safety.", "Water-Resistant and Non-Greasy: Provides durable protection with a quick-drying formula that rubs on clear and leaves no residue.", "Cosmetic-Friendly: Free from titanium dioxide and zinc oxide, making it ideal for use under makeup and other cosmetics.", "Convenient Carabiner: Easily clips onto bags, belts, or keyrings, ensuring you’re always prepared on the go.", "Compact 30ml Size: Perfect for travel, outdoor activities, or keeping handy in your everyday essentials."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "3.8 cm (w) x 9.3 cm (h)"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "White", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/pssun02/pssun02-white.webp"}]'::jsonb,null,'supplier',true,false,null,5,'local_stock','Intex','https://www.intexglobal.com/product/30ml-spf50-sunscreen-lotion-with-carabiner/');
