  ('IntexGlobal','SCSE04','Padded Nylon Stadium Cushion Sport Product','padded-nylon-stadium-cushion-sport-product-scse04','Outdoor & Lifestyle','Sports Products','The Padded Nylon Stadium Cushion is a high-quality, lightweight, and portable seating solution, designed to provide extra comfort during games, outdoor events, and concerts. Made from durable nylon with soft padding, this cushion helps relieve pressure from hard seating surfaces, making it a must-have for sports fans and event-goers.',250,true,false,'["Premium Nylon Material: Durable and resistant to wear and tear.", "Padded for Extra Comfort: Provides cushioning for extended seating.", "Lightweight & Portable: Easy to carry and store.", "Perfect for Stadiums & Outdoor Events: Ideal for sports games, concerts, picnics, and camping.", "Easy to Clean: Wipeable surface for hassle-free maintenance.", "Custom Branding Available: Can be printed with logos or designs for promotional use."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "30 (w) x 30 (h) x 3 (d) cm"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Black", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/scse04/scse04-black.webp"}, {"name": "Navy", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/scse04/scse04-navy.webp"}, {"name": "Royal Blue", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/scse04/scse04-royal-blue.webp"}]'::jsonb,null,'supplier',true,true,5.32,28,'indent_sea','Intex','https://www.intexglobal.com/product/padded-nylon-stadium-cushion/');
