  ('IntexGlobal','STRS41','Earth Stress Shape Stress Ball & Toy','earth-stress-shape-stress-ball-toy-strs41','Toys & Games','Stress Balls & Toys','The Earth Stress Shape is a unique and engaging stress-relief tool, designed to promote environmental awareness and global branding. Made from high-quality polyurethane foam, this soft and squeezable stress ball features a detailed Earth design, making it an ideal promotional giveaway for eco-friendly campaigns, travel promotions, and corporate events.',250,true,false,'["Earth-Shaped Design: Perfect for environmental and global branding.", "Helps Relieve Stress & Tension: Ideal for office workers, students, and event attendees.", "Compact & Lightweight: Easy to carry and store.", "Great for Eco-Friendly & Travel Promotions: Perfect for businesses promoting sustainability, education, or international outreach."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "6.3 (d) cm"}, {"name": "Durable Polyurethane Foam", "value": "Soft, squeezable, and long-lasting."}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Default", "hex": "", "image": ""}]'::jsonb,null,'supplier',true,true,0.93,28,'indent_sea','Intex','https://www.intexglobal.com/product/earth-stress-shape/');
