  ('IntexGlobal','UMBR07','London Business Umbrella','london-business-umbrella-umbr07','Outdoor & Lifestyle','Umbrellas','The London Business Umbrella offers a sleek and professional look, perfect for corporate settings or everyday use. This 23-inch, 8-bone long-handled umbrella features a durable black fibre frame reinforced with a steel middle rod for superior strength. Its 190T encrypted impact fabric provides excellent protection against the elements, while the automatic opening mechanism allows for quick deploym',250,true,false,'["23-inch canopy with 8-bone structure.", "Long-handled automatic opening, manual closing.", "Black fibre frame with steel middle rod for durability.", "190T encrypted impact fabric for weather resistance.", "Classic black plastic bent handle for comfort and style."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "69 (h) cm"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Black", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/umbr07/umbr07-black.webp"}, {"name": "Blue", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/umbr07/umbr07-blue.webp"}, {"name": "Green", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/umbr07/umbr07-green.webp"}, {"name": "Orange", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/umbr07/umbr07-orange.webp"}, {"name": "Pink", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/umbr07/umbr07-pink.webp"}, {"name": "Red", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/umbr07/umbr07-red.webp"}, {"name": "White", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/umbr07/umbr07-white.webp"}, {"name": "Yellow", "hex":