  ('IntexGlobal','WPPB01','Full Colour Printed Conference Bag','full-colour-printed-conference-bag-wppb01','Bags','Tote Bags','The Full Colour Printed Conference Bag is a high-impact promotional tote, ideal for trade shows, corporate events, and conferences. Made from 80gsm non-woven material, this laminated tote bag offers full-colour branding with contrast trim and handles for a sleek and professional look.',1,true,false,'["Full-Colour Laminated Printing: Provides a bold and eye-catching design for maximum brand exposure.", "Durable 80gsm Non-Woven Material: Lightweight yet sturdy for carrying event materials, brochures, and essentials.", "Contrast Trim & Handles: Stylish design enhances the overall aesthetic appeal.", "Spacious Interior: Ideal for conference materials, documents, and promotional items.", "Large Branding Area: Perfect for logos, slogans, and event messaging in vibrant full-colour print."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "30 (w) x 37 (h)  x 10 (d) cm"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Custom", "hex": "", "image": ""}]'::jsonb,null,'supplier',true,true,null,28,'indent_sea','Intex','https://www.intexglobal.com/product/full-colour-printed-conference-bag/');
